clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b777c9f8ca0a5a37f29622aa26157e9ee9c3d2a","tid":1367912,"uid":186882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:37:31.000Z","msg":"你隔離係共產黨<br />\n你唔攪革命味下一代受<br />\n況且而家既有利益組織有哂利益<br />\n唔清算邊個做特首都一樣"},{"pid":"b742f2cc2e0ff944c950f9af66958600ed906374","tid":1367912,"uid":30791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9e2433a2d7fcd122c6c784b8ebccd55e43631cf6","tid":1367912,"uid":81716,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:35:36.000Z","msg":"請唔好Spin 左去搵人做特首，五大訴求都未解決又搵人做特首？仲咁天真覺得搵個人上去就解決到問題？<br />\n<br />\n由老董下台，大家期望曾蔭權解決所有野當佢救世主，結果高地價，由佢接任到離任，令到地價係咁升，買唔起樓<br />\n<br />\n到佢下台之後，689 同唐唐，d人驚揀唐唐會好似曾蔭權咁行更高地價，揀隻狼好過揀隻豬，起完全唔估佢往續就揀左佢上去，結果係點，大家好清楚<br />\n<br />\n由689 到777 又一樣一開波有蜜月期，話自己唔係與民為敵，之後又係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到依家你地又有種期望，換左條友會好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/